cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper presents a deep learning framework for solving a locomotion task, which involves reinforcement learning and robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the injection of external experiences, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper uses simulation environments and discusses the agent's ability to adapt to obstacles, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision).
